title: Kingroot 5.3.0 build 187 (One Click Root) - 2017 - ArmaanPC
description:
Kingroot 5.3.0 build 187 (One Click Root) - 2017 - ArmaanPC

KingRoot- The best application for getting Root rights right on your device. KingRoot can come in handy when you do not have a custom recovery (TWRP, CWM) for your phone or you have a bootloader disabled.

Easy, fast and without a computer! Starting with version 4.5.0, the application positions itself, like everything in one (KingRoot + KingUser). In addition to controlling Root access in KingRoot, there are many useful features: removal of system applications, startup management, phone cleaning, notification control, virus protection. KingRoot PC supports more than 10,000 mobile phones and 40,000 firmware. For example, such devices as Samsung, Nexus, Mi, ZTE, Huawei and other popular models and firmware in the Android 2.2-6.0 range.

When Root rights are received via the mobile version, KNOX does not work and there is a chance to disable Sony_RIC protection. How to use KingRoot:1. Turn on the Internet. (Wi-Fi / 3G, etc.) 2. Install the KingRoot. 3. Get a Root. (Wait for 100%) 4. Restart the device. If you lost Root, just reboot and run KingRoot.
